OL,3,CCharge dropped against policeman
OL,4,Caccused of sexual offence aged 12
OL,6,FA Guernsey policeman accused of a
OL,7,Fhistorical sexual offence has had the
OL,8,Fcharge against him dropped.
OL,10,FThe serving officer, who has not been
OL,11,Fnamed, was arrested in August and
OL,12,Fimmediately suspended from duty.
OL,14,FA joint statement from Guernsey Police
OL,15,Fand the Law Officers says the reported
OL,16,Fcrime is alleged to have taken place
OL,17,Fwhen the man was around 12 years of
OL,18,Fage, the current age of criminal
OL,19,Fresponsibility, and this was a
OL,20,F"relevant factor" in the decision not
OL,21,Fto prosecute.
