OL,6,FThe police misconduct process has also
OL,7,Ffinished and the officer's suspension
OL,8,Fhas been lifted with immediate effect.
OL,10,FThe joint statement explains: "A
OL,11,Fthorough criminal investigation has
OL,12,Fbeen undertaken. The evidence in the
OL,13,Fcase was referred to the Law Officers
OL,14,Fof the Crown to decide whether the
OL,15,Fmatter would be subject to a criminal
OL,16,Fprosecution.
