OL,6,F"We'd continue to encourage anyone who
OL,7,Fhas been the victim of a sexual
OL,8,Foffence, recent or historic, to come
OL,9,Fforward to police.
OL,11,F"We will thoroughly investigate all
OL,12,Fcases and rigorously pursue offenders
OL,13,Fof this nature, and it remains a
OL,14,Fpriority for us as an organisation."
